snippet.title: HTR: Hyper Torque Racing on Steam
snippet.description:
"HTR: Hyper Torque Racing," a racing game with easy controls that lets you experience realistic racing, is now on Steam.
You can enjoy single-player as well as online PvP with up to 8 players. Win intense races and become the world's best racer.

Steam Store: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3181120/HTR/
Offical Website: https://hypertorqueracing.com/
Twitter : https://twitter.com/HyperTrqRacing
